Class FilterAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.webcodepro.applecommander.ui.swt.filteradapter.FilterAdapter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ApplesoftFilterAdapter, BusinessBASICFilterAdapter, GraphicsFilterAdapter, TextFilterAdapter

    public abstract class FilterAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a visual adapter for a FileFilter. Generally, the display method is the only variance between the many FileFilters available.
